{"tid":1987581,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"中國女生是不是真的惹不起？","createTime":"2020-04-24T14:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T14:33:52.000Z","uid":252078,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59a5bd9ce83c3500b50a4fea93e588d7d53ed281","tid":1987581,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"被封為「亞洲舞王」的羅志祥昨（23）日被交往九年的前女友周揚青爆出分手內幕，指控羅志祥常背著她四處約妹，還與旗下女藝人、化妝師有長期不正當的男女關係，甚至還經常舉行「多人運動」，種種行為讓周揚青直呼「顛覆三觀」引發外界砲轟，羅志祥形象大受打擊。對此就有網友好奇「中國女生是不是真的惹不起？」貼文發出後引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n該名網友在PTT八卦版發文表示想當年周揚青只是羅志祥的一個小粉絲，每周為了他從中國飛來台灣，看起來就像個傻妹，結果真的分開要報復的時候，直接讓羅志祥跟他身邊的人黑爆，「感覺整件事都是精心策劃過的，這麼一想中國女生是不是真的惹不起，要讓你死的時候就會讓你一次摔死？」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RJXDLLx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJXDLLx.jpg&h=8b7a97e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/maeuSqO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaeuSqO.jpg&h=c73e9744&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18b7fc3cb1025d3d2cbe588a84f349889839194b","tid":1987581,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:29:23.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20200424/4053462/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20200424%2F4053462%2F&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=d08cfa3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20200424/4053462/</a>"},{"pid":"5838ed443326a39e0719e9eae8ce2c648348fdd3","tid":1987581,"uid":88374,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:30:15.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n睇啲藍絲廢老俾支那老婆呃家產就知"},{"pid":"c130adb4d35d34b65156f9f9cf0d1c6773a18038","tid":1987581,"uid":65638,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"自細鬥慣，根本佢圩個成長環境就係咁，好正常"}]}